candidates.title: Writer refactor
candidates.body:
Since I wasn't able to prepare the #37 in one go, I decided to iteratively get to that point.

This change refactors `ChunkWriter` into more generic asynchronous-io. At some point, all operations should go through it. Then it will accept a "backend object" that instead of using FS operations, will do HTTP requests etc. and work will be complete.
